---
/**
 * SchemaOrg.astro
 *
 * Sitewide structured data for mkultraman.com.
 *
 * Emits a single @graph containing:
 *   - Organization (the consulting practice)
 *   - ProfessionalService (LocalBusiness subtype)
 *   - Person (Tetsu, founder)
 *   - Three Service nodes (Stack Audit, Infrastructure Build, Ongoing Management)
 *   - WebSite with SearchAction
 *   - The Guild Organization (cross-site network)
 *   - WebSite entries for all guild member sites
 *
 * Inject this component inside <head> in Base.astro.
 */

